data.description: Nice 2 story home! Inside, you will find open living/dining/kitchen spaces with granite counters, a breakfast bar, and a large, double door pantry in the kitchen. Downstairs there is also a bedroom and bathroom tucked away, perfect for a private guest space or home office. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a laundry room, and a massive bonus room that could be used as a second living space, play room, or anything else you can dream up. A LOT to enjoy!
